Slow down, my feet hurt.

01:03.497 --> 01:06.899
All right, Irene,
just remember
that we are Greek, okay?

01:06.901 --> 01:11.136
I'm going to do all
the talking, we have to
get into this party.

01:11.138 --> 01:12.838
