thank you very much

02:05.726 --> 02:07.559
and he was very cute.

02:07.561 --> 02:11.697
Okay, what I remember is...
you showed up in the meeting
you couldn't come out of after.

02:11.699 --> 02:16.568
Well, you've to admit,
life is more fun
when you've got goals.

02:16.570 --> 02:18.537
It is goals.

02:20.140 --> 02:22.174
What are we gonna do now?

04:34.807 --> 04:38.910
<i>Do people from Brazil</i>
<i>desperately wanna travel</i>
<i>to New Jersey?</i>

