12:16.069 --> 12:17.569
That's gross.

12:17.571 --> 12:20.271
- That's gross.
- That's the job.

12:21.741 --> 12:29.414
Why does it always seem
like everything fabulous
is so far away from me.

12:29.416 --> 12:32.517
And I think,
it's all right there
in your head.

12:32.519 --> 12:36.020
<i>Ladies</i>
<i>and Gentlemen,</i>
<i>an important announcement...</i>

12:40.292 --> 12:43.428
