I'm not a invalid.

15:39.339 --> 15:42.640
So, please,
do not treat me like one.

15:43.809 --> 15:47.345
If you want to be useful...

15:47.347 --> 15:52.050
you can bring-in that poor
resina plant out there.

15:52.052 --> 15:53.618
Bring her inside.

15:58.390 --> 16:02.360
