please hurry.

16:02.362 --> 16:06.631
I don't
think, this is fire wood yet,

16:06.633 --> 16:08.666
but I can try to
use your hammer.

16:08.668 --> 16:11.502
No, Dora, it will come back.

16:11.504 --> 16:14.272
And then we'll put it in the sun
where it belongs.

16:20.679 --> 16:22.313
