16:26.852 --> 16:30.088
Can I...
can make you a cup of tea?

16:32.558 --> 16:33.658
No, tea.

16:38.397 --> 16:40.398
No... tea.

16:45.237 --> 16:49.340
-Aunt Vera, would you
like a drink?
-Martini dry with a twist.

16:49.342 --> 16:51.642
Yes, ma'am.
Cocktail comin' up.

17:02.087 --> 17:03.755
I-I love your home.

17:05.790 --> 17:07.492
Does it have a name?

17:07.493 --> 17:11.796
